OL,4,G0100FFred Dibnah's Industrial Age
OL,5,     GFred Dibnah takes a look at
OL,6,     Gmining, touring from Cornwall to
OL,7,     GScotland to explore how tin,
OL,8,     Gslate, lead and coal were all
OL,9,     Gextracted from the ground.
OL,10,G0130FCanal Boat Diaries
OL,11,     GThe real side of boat life with
OL,12,     GRobbie Cumming. Robbie runs
OL,13,     Gaground on the Rochdale Canal -
OL,14,     Gwill he make it to Manchester?
OL,15,G0200FFace the Music
OL,16,     GJoseph Cooper invites viewers to
OL,17,     Gmatch their musical wits against
OL,18,     Gguests Annette Page, Richard
OL,19,     GBaker and Robin Ray. With guest
OL,20,     Gmusician Murray Perahia.
